(3729, 'At a land mass of 9,970,610 square kilimeters, Canada is ___ than the Russian Federation.', '["smallest","smaller","as small"]', 'smaller', '', 0, 2, 'http://a4esl.org/q/j/dt/mc-canada1.html'),
