(3946, 'Can you think of an animal that is distinguished ___ its greed?', '["over","by","on","of"]', 'by', 'To indicate a mean or method, we use the preposition BY.', 1, 3, 'http://a4esl.org/q/j/tp/mc-particle3.html'),
